\vec{F}
\vec{F}(r,\theta,\varphi)
F_{r}=2ar\sin(\theta)\sin(\varphi),\:  F_{\theta}=ar\cos(\theta)\sin(\varphi),\: F_{\varphi}=ar\cos(\varphi)
\nabla\times \vec{F}=\vec{0}
\nabla=\frac{\partial \hat{\boldsymbol{\imath}}}{\partial x}+\frac{\partial \hat{\boldsymbol{\jmath}}}{\partial y}+\frac{\partial \hat{\boldsymbol{k}}}{\partial z}
